r added to the library`, other: t`${folders.length} folders added to the library`, }); toastsAPI.add('success', message); await libraryAPI.scan(); invalidate(); } } else { setIsShown(false); } }) .catch(logAndNotifyError); return unlisten; } const unlisten = attachFileDropEvent().catch(logAndNotifyError); return function cleanup() { unlisten.then((u) => (u ? u() : null)); }; }, [ libraryAPI.addLibraryFolders, libraryAPI.scan, toastsAPI.add, invalidate, t, ]); const classes = cx(styles.dropzone, { [styles.shown]: isShown, }); return ( <div className={classes}> <div className={styles.dropzoneTitle}>{t`Add music to the library`}</div> <span>{t`Drop folders anywhere`}</span> </div> ); } 
